data.title: Famous People Who Died in 1214
data.meta_description: Famous deaths in 1214. Learn about 6 historical figures, notable people and celebrities who died in 1214 or search by date or keyword.
data.text:
Eustaes van Machelen, Flemish knight, dies in the Battle of Bouvines

Jul 27 Stefan van Longchamp, French knight, dies in the Battle of Bouvines

Albert Avogadro, Italian patriarch of Jerusalem (b. 1149)

Alfonso VIII the Noble, King of Castile and Toledo (1158-1214), dies at 58

Eleanor of England, Queen consort of Castile and Toledo (1170-1214), daughter of Henry II, King of England, and Eleanor of Aquitaine, dies at 53

William I "the Lion", King of Scotland (1165-1214)
